cosmetica.rsewarning.title: Do you want to enable Region-Specific Effects?
cosmetica.rsewarning.description: §7Region-Specific Effects applies extra exclusive cosmetics based on what country you're in. For example, Australians will be turned uʍop ǝpısdn ;). While this is a lot of fun, it does mean that players can use this to determine your country of origin. If you disable Region-Specific effects, you won't be able to see the effects on others either.
